"""
        Test that a DeviceCredential struct missing media identifier data can
        be written to a data stream.
        """
credential = objects.DeviceCredential(device_serial_number='serNum123456',
    password='secret', device_identifier='devID2233', network_identifier=
    'netID9000', machine_identifier='machineID1')
stream = utils.BytearrayStream()
credential.write(stream)
self.assertEqual(len(self.encoding_missing_media_identifier), len(stream))
self.assertEqual(str(self.encoding_missing_media_identifier), str(stream))
